      "writtenOn": "2026-03-09T17:08:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you have any opinion on the matter? I think it\u0027s quite convenient to have one file per class and also helps to quickly find the relevant files.\n\nIt can also help to avoid git conflicts and does not require us to make a choice as to the order of the classes inside the file.\n\nIt also helps to avoid including more than what is necessary.",
